{"tid":886204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"GDP差距拉近 中國5年內可望超美","createTime":"2018-11-02T02:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T15:28:48.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"51f8be3db890269a3a94f1ec5abf4b08869d82eb","tid":886204,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:32:50.000Z","msg":"中國歷經40年的改革與開放後，國內生產毛額（GDP）成長速度可說是三級跳，1978年，中國邁出改革開放第一步時，當年美國GDP總量是中國的15.7倍，時至2017年，中美的GDP差距倍數已縮小至1.6倍。一般預料中國GDP總量最多5年就會跑贏美國。<br />\n<br />\n2017年全球各國GDP總量超過10兆美元大關，只有美國與中國，美國是19.36兆美元，中國有12.25兆美元，雙方差距已縮小至1.6倍。對比1978年，雙方的差距高達15.7倍，中國的經濟實力歷經40年改革與開放的努力，實力已非當年的吳下阿蒙。<br />\n<br />\n目前全球其他國家很難追趕中美兩國的GDP總量，以排名第3大經濟體的日本，2017年GDP總量是4.88兆美元，只有中國GDP的4成，雙方總量差距達7兆美元。據專家預測，2018年，美國的GDP總量突破20兆美元大關，而中國也將突破14兆美元。<br />\n<br />\n中國在2008年金融海嘯前的2007年，躍居全球第3大經濟體，金融海嘯後的2010年則榮登第2大經濟體，差美國僅有一步之遙。根據推估，以中國目前的GDP成長速度看，最多5年，中國可望跑贏美國登頂，躋身全球最大經濟體。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20181102000107-260309\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Fnewspapers%2F20181102000107-260309&d=1VJWldnTnQw7AQGwQpx2r10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=8a890c56\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20181102000107-260309</a>"},{"pid":"6edef4587db383e6bf024f1ecf26ccf49294fbac","tid":886204,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:33:57.000Z","msg":"GDP作咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388ce83aee0e688a325781a90050d7001a0ab505","tid":886204,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6edef4587db383e6bf024f1ecf26ccf49294fbac","tid":886204,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:33:57.000Z","msg":"GDP作咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:35:11.000Z","msg":"佢話而家已經超過美帝都得啦，d水份多撚到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603233afcb8c4aa60c8d7381d31facce11ea9d53","tid":886204,"uid":58552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:35:37.000Z","msg":"好 出師更有名"},{"pid":"518d65dffbdbc180d4d84864874df9e3736ac7fa","tid":886204,"uid":53687,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:37:36.000Z","msg":"咁犀厲呀！加重啲關稅先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f2e861430c7f726a96134f937401f6b46e6dcf","tid":886204,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:38:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec148cab4f89be67c203031ef6b30a40cb43e3eb","tid":886204,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"侵侵驚呆了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a344da951184c25ae16eb770bf32c3b6dbbc51","tid":886204,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T14:55:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fyN6TUN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfyN6TUN.png&h=ccfd1950&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb8317ce20cbd4a53f81591060eaf4f0b186ad79","tid":886204,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"518d65dffbdbc180d4d84864874df9e3736ac7fa","tid":886204,"uid":53687,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:37:36.000Z","msg":"咁犀厲呀！加重啲關稅先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T15:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305b3e052a3990ceb9ad561a3a3978b17c7241fb","tid":886204,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T15:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/02/231758_0a6726f3b202eeb76dff84568dc76c39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F02%2F231758_0a6726f3b202eeb76dff84568dc7